{"tid":480641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO唔洗平權，但可唔可以叫英國幫我地爭取多D免簽","createTime":"2017-11-26T10:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T16:11:14.000Z","uid":109077,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"558cd5dd77b155ffff0f966df23574f2e4bb3bd1","tid":480641,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得平權真係冇咩可能<br />\n雖然香港人好優秀，但對英國人黎講始終係外族<br />\n反而依家我地可以做既係叫返英國爭取多D免簽<br />\n<br />\n幾年前英國宣佈唔會再單方面主動為BNO爭取免簽<br />\n老實講如果真係只計旅遊，特區比BNO好用<br />\n而英國的確係有義務為BNO爭取返免簽<br />\n<br />\n香港人其實幾慘，係已發展地區中唯一一個冇美國免簽<br />\n全世界免簽數連東歐垃圾國家都不如<br />\n反而韓國依家已經超越日本成為世界第二多免簽國家<br />\n同香港各種指數相似既新加坡更加已經係世界第一多免簽國家<br />\n<br />\nBNO有佢既優勢<br />\n因為人數少、唔會再比非香港人申請<br />\n再加上香港本身冇宗教問題、冇歷史衝突、人既質素高<br />\n完全係有資格拎到更多國家既免簽<br />\n既然特區因為中國人既關係而冇得改，不如從BNO入手"},{"pid":"1f93f25c87bf4270835482614c056f4b2483f749","tid":480641,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f36775966f844dc4d968ce666ce9458567bd6e1","tid":480641,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e37abddbd65097302f2d0e5e1b5e7dafd4c3286a","tid":480641,"uid":109077,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人好優秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己都睇自己唔起唔好同人講港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4aee5b7809f875672f28439b6358c471ef7c050","tid":480641,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi