fc7f871fce574356bdc5f17ee5be3c3c1358788","tid":480641,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港人好優秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己都睇自己唔起唔好同人講港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個隻支那澳門狗黎<br />\n唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我揸葡籍架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講支那點都唔及你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望下你本護照先再出聲啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎護照打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得澳門搞到第三世界咁"},{"pid":"54531e43a5442c01c5b9f09cf5c6dfa6c68bbb5c","tid":480641,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77093f62bedff09f820b1fe0a94e9d98000fe881","tid":480641,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:02:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffdc3cc768911150bc1d0bd23eda355eb03a5a5d","tid":480641,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"人既質素高<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f45ebeaccd1c83e14feb296ce33e189198e0111","tid":480641,"uid":128014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港人好優秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo